Nc6 4. Nf3 Nf6 5. Nbd2 ({I have a specific reason for choosing this move order 
as opposed to 5. c3. The point is to counter ...Qb6. After} 5. c3 Qb6 $1 {is 
awkward. I think Qb3 never really favours White in this variation and the 
